OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1778367989
OL,3,CMan arrested after car ploughs into
OL,4,Cpeople in Nottinghamshire town
OL,5,Cinjuring five
OL,7,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,8,Fof attempted murder after a car crash
OL,9,Finto multiple pedestrians in a
OL,10,FNottinghamshire town centre, with one
OL,11,Fman sustaining life-threatening
OL,12,Finjuries
OL,14,FEmergency services were called to
OL,15,FMarket Place in Arnold at 1.12am today
OL,16,F(9 May) following reports a red
OL,17,FVauxhall Astra had struck a group of
OL,18,Fpeople.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
