FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1778367989
OL,3,CMan arrested after car ploughs into
OL,4,Cpeople in Nottinghamshire town
OL,5,Cinjuring five
OL,7,FOne man remains in hospital with life-
OL,8,Fthreatening injuries, while four other
OL,9,Fmen suffered minor injuries.
OL,11,FA 40-year-old man is being held by
OL,12,FNottinghamshire Police on suspicion of
OL,13,Fattempted murder after he was arrested
OL,14,Fthis evening.
OL,16,FNottinghamshire Police has said
OL,17,FCounter Terrorism Police are not
OL,18,Finvolved in the investigation.
OL,20,FDetective Chief Inspector Ruby Burrow,
OL,21,Fwho is leading the investigation, said:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1778367989
OL,3,CMan arrested after car ploughs into
OL,4,Cpeople in Nottinghamshire town
OL,5,Cinjuring five
OL,7,F"We have shared this important update
OL,8,Fwith the family of the seriously
OL,9,Finjured man and they are being
OL,10,Fsupported by specialist officers.
OL,12,F"We would ask that people do not
OL,13,Fspeculate about the circumstances
OL,14,Faround the incident and respect the
OL,15,Fprivacy of those involved.
OL,17,F"Our investigation remains ongoing and
OL,18,Fwe are keeping an open mind while
OL,19,Fthese extensive inquiries continue.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1778367989
OL,3,CMan arrested after car ploughs into
OL,4,Cpeople in Nottinghamshire town
OL,5,Cinjuring five
OL,7,F"We'd like to thank those members of
OL,8,Fthe public who have shared information
OL,9,Fwith us but still want to hear from
OL,10,Fanyone else who can assist.
OL,12,F"Anyone who has relevant dashcam,
OL,13,FCCTV, doorbell or mobile phone footage
OL,14,Fshould also get in touch and share it
OL,15,Fwith the investigation team.
OL,17,F"All road closures in the area have
OL,18,Fnow been lifted and we'd like to thank
OL,19,Flocal people for their understanding."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU{D@fO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
