OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1778367989
OL,3,CMan arrested after car ploughs into
OL,4,Cpeople in Nottinghamshire town
OL,5,Cinjuring five
OL,7,FSeveral road closures are in place
OL,8,Faround Arnold town centre as police
OL,9,Finvestigate the incident. Market
OL,10,FPlace, as well as the junctions from
OL,11,FGedling Road to Derby Street, Hallam's
OL,12,FLane and Central Avenue are closed off.
OL,14,FPolice said the closures will remain
OL,15,Fin place for some time and have urged
OL,16,Fmotorists to avoid the area where
OL,17,Fpossible. Anyone who witnessed the
OL,18,Fincident or has information relating
OL,19,Fto what happened is urged to share it
OL,20,Fwith the police.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
